of%20four-lane%20Paramakudi-Ramanathapuram%20Section%20of%20NH-87%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C853%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-approves-4-lane-paramakudi-ramanathapuram-road-project-in-tamil-nadu-8807239%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20bought%20a%20nearly%20100-year-old%20skyscraper%20in%20Chicago%20and%20want%20to%20preserve%20its%20identity%20while%20making%20a%20few%20changes.%20Here's%20what%20I%20plan%20to%20do.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20on%20top%20of%20a%20skyscraper%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ba13f748d8c055f4a545%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Liravongsa%20atop%20the%20Pittsfield%20Building%20in%20Chicago.%3Cp%3ESkyscraper%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvestor%20Tom%20Liravongsa%20is%20renovating%20a%20landmarked%20skyscraper%20into%20an%20apartment%20building.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20building%2C%20built%20in%201927%2C%20was%20once%20a%20major%20medical%20office%20and%20is%20now%20mostly%20vacant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELiravongsa%20thinks%20the%20classic%20craftsmanship%20will%20make%20it%20stand%20out%20from%20other%20residential%20buildings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tom%20Liravongsa%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fskyscraperguy%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETom%20the%20Skyscraper%20Guy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20investor%20who%20purchased%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20Pittsfield%20Building%2C%20a%2038-story%20skyscraper%20in%20Chicago%20that%20has%20been%20partially%20vacant%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade.%20Liravongsa%20is%20turning%20the%20former%20office%20building%20into%20residences.%20The%20building%20was%20built%20in%201927%20and%20landmarked%20in%202002.%20The%20conversations%20have%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20building%20has%20quite%20a%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20in%20disarray%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20if%20you%20dive%20into%20the%20real%20history%20of%20it%2C%20it's%20gone%20through%20so%20much%20turmoil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20knew%20that%20it%20was%20a%20Marshall%20Field%20estate%20building.%20It%20was%20built%20by%20Marshall%20Fields%20III%2C%20and%20prior%20to%20it%20becoming%20a%20disarray%2C%20I%20think%20the%20last%20lease%20burned%20in%202017.%20Prior%20to%20that%2C%20it%20was%20the%20largest%20medical%20office%20east%20of%20the%20Mississippi%20with%20775%20doctors%20and%20dentists%20in%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20copper%20top%20of%20a%20skyscraper%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862baf285e81483682d0c73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pittsfield%20Building%20was%20built%20in%201927.%3Cp%3ESkyscraper%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20in%20Jewelers%20Row%2C%20which%20is%20a%20really%20prominent%20area%20for%20selling%20high-end%20jewelry.%20In%20fact%2C%20we%20discovered%20recently%20that%20on%20the%20sixth%20floor%2C%20there's%20a%20store%20that%20sold%20pearl%20jewelry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20remnants%20that%20we've%20just%20been%20discovering%2C%20you%20wouldn't%20have%20found%20them%20unless%20you%20were%20in%20the%20building.%20There%20are%20safes%20that%20were%20built%20into%20the%20wall%20and%20compressors%20in%20the%20basement%20specifically%20for%20compressed%20air%20for%20doctors%20and%20dentists%20to%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20grotesques%20on%20the%20corners%20of%20the%20building.%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20they%20were%20there%20until%20we%20were%20literally%20hanging%20over%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220602453a-e9df-4bbf-bbfd-44977280e076%5C%22%3EI%20bought%2080%25%20of%20the%20building%20for%20about%20%247%20million%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20COVID%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20at%20basically%20all%20markets%20that%20had%20office%20spaces%2C%20knowing%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20shift%20in%20how%20office%20space%20is%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20is%20the%20Midwest%20close%20to%20home%2C%20but%20I'm%20very%20familiar%20with%20Chicago.%20I've%20been%20here%20long%20enough%20to%20know%20Chicago%20is%20also%20a%20developer-friendly%20city%20when%20you're%20doing%20the%20right%20things%2C%20which%20is%20residential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20what%20we're%20doing.%20We're%20changing%20an%20office%20building%20into%20a%20residential%20building%2C%20and%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20come%20along%20with%20doing%20something%20like%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20acquired%20the%20building%20in%20May%202023.%20We%20had%20actually%20purchased%20it%20out%20of%20a%20foreclosure%2C%20so%20that's%20how%20we%20were%20able%20to%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20standing%20on%20a%20scissor%20lift%20beneath%20a%20chandelier.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862bbaf3d5881a51c1c5df8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELiravongsa%20owns%2080%25%20of%20the%20building.%3Cp%3ESkyscraper%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20paid%20just%20over%20%247.5%20million%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20own%2080%25%20of%20the%20building%20now.%20When%20I%20say%20we%2C%20yes%2C%20it's%20investors%2C%20and%20the%20investors%20are%20your%20partners.%20Most%20people%20would%20be%20familiar%20with%20something%20like%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20they%20have%20vertically%20bifurcated%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20same%20situation%20that%20you%20have%20here%20in%20Chicago.%20So%2C%20we%20own%20everything%20except%20floors%2013%20to%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20it%20was%20office%20space.%20I%20believe%20they%20started%20doing%20conversions%20in%202009.%20The%20building%20currently%20has%20228%20apartments%2C%20which%20are%20about%2080%25%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20are%20active%20market-rate%20apartments%20that%20are%20located%20on%20floors%2010%20to%2021.%20We%20have%20three%20floors%20of%20apartments%2C%20and%20the%20floors%20we%20don't%20own%20are%20all%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20sitting%20on%20top%20of%20a%20skyscraper%20in%20Chicago.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862bc17f748d8c055f4a582%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Pittsfield%20Building%20has%2038%20floors.%3Cp%3ESkyscraper%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20is%20now%20just%20completely%20vacant.%20And%20that's%20what%20we%20are%20working%20through%20and%20getting%20turned%20into%20apartments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20still%20have%20some%20mixed-use%2C%20meaning%20we'll%20have%20retail-floor%20activation%2C%20and%20we'll%20have%20basement%20activation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20importantly%2C%20for%20100%20years%2C%20people%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20see%20this%20building%20for%20what%20it%20is%20%E2%80%94%20this%20craftsmanship%20specifically.%20They've%20not%20been%20able%20to%20see%20things%20such%20as%20the%20copper%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we're%20offering%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20viewing%20to%20the%20public%2C%20like%20a%20museum%20inside%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209ebe4f2-8ab4-482f-ba79-d0ed82abdbe0%5C%22%3EI%20want%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20classic%20craftsmanship%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20developers%20come%20in%20and%20they%20just%20want%20to%20make%20it%20their%20own%20%E2%80%94%20and%20their%20own%20is%20going%20with%20what%20they%20think%20the%20market%20is%2C%20which%20is%20like%20a%20glass%20tower.%20We're%20building%20glass%20towers%20now%2C%20and%20they're%20nowhere%20near%20the%20attention%20and%20the%20allure%20that%20this%20building%20has.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20been%20a%20real%20shift%20in%20the%20market%20to%20what%20we%20call%20themed%20buildings%20because%20these%20conversions%20are%20happening%2C%20and%20a%20themed%20building%20%E2%80%94%20like%20this%201920s%20craftsmanship%20building%20%E2%80%94%20has%20its%20own%20allure%20outside%20being%20a%20glass%20tower.%20Anybody%20can%20go%20and%20live%20in%20a%20glass%20tower%3B%20there's%20nothing%20exciting%20about%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20have%20this%20building%20with%20all%20of%20these%20features%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20reference%20them%2C%20there's%20something%20to%20be%20said%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20modernize%20different%20components%2C%20you'll%20have%20amenity%20spaces%20that%20will%20be%20a%20mixture%20of%20modern%20and%20also%20maintain%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20craftsmanship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holding%20a%20light%20standing%20in%20an%20elevator%20lobby.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862bb4ef748d8c055f4a568%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20building%20is%20landmarked%2C%20and%20Liravongsa%20wants%20to%20keep%20its%201920s%20charm.%3Cp%3ESkyscraper%20Media%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hallways%20and%20other%20areas%20will%20be%20very%20much%20maintained%2C%20but%20some%20of%20the%20interior%20units%20might%20be%20a%20little%20more%20modern.%20But%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20modern%2C%20we're%20thinking%20about%20the%20basics%3A%20the%20way%20your%20doors%20and%20windows%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20talking%20about%20how%20HVAC%20and%20other%20systems%20are%20going%20to%20be%20modernized.%20Those%20are%20basic%20modernizations%2C%20but%20you%20can%20still%20incorporate%20those%20behind%20walls%20so%20you%20can%20keep%20the%20allure%20of%20these%20older%20buildings%20without%20having%20to%20change%20them%20per%20se.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20of%20the%20commercial%20real%20estate%20market%20right%20now%20is%20that%20there%20is%20empty%20office%20space.%20We%20were%20just%20introduced%20to%20another%20WeWork-style%20space%2C%20completely%20empty%20%E2%80%94%20six%20floors%20of%20it.%20We%20were%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20this%20is%20such%20a%20sad%20thing.%26quot%3B%20I%20remember%20a%20time%20when%20I%20thought%2C%20I%20would%20love%20to%20be%20in%20an%20office%20like%20this.%20Now%20there's%20no%20one%20in%20those%20offices.%20And%20so%20the%20question%20is%2C%20what%20do%20we%20do%20with%20those%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20a%20maximized%20residential%20building.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20Chicago%20has%20one%20of%20the%20best%20job%20markets%20in%20the%20Midwest.%20It's%20a%20hub%2C%20but%20there%20are%20also%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20live%20here.%20You%20don't%20need%20an%20office%20right%20now%3B%20we%20need%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-98-year-old-chicago-skyscraper-what-i-plan-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751364541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862ba2c85e81483682d0c56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-98-year-old-chicago-skyscraper-what-i-plan-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tom%20Liravongsa%20wants%20to%20turn%20a%20historic%20Chicago%20skyscraper%20into%20apartments%20while%