0They%20are%2024%20kms%20away%20from%20Nagpur.%20I%20worked%20on%20a%2010-hectare%20polluted%20wasteland%20and%20in%20two%20years%20it%20was%20rejuvenated%20and%20in%20four%20years%20it%20was%20ready%20for%20crop%20cultivation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStep%20by%20step%2C%20project%20by%20project%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20and%20his%20team%20proved%20that%20barren%2C%20damaged%20lands%20could%20be%20saved.%20This%20was%20no%20quick%20fix%E2%80%94it%20took%20years%20of%20planting%2C%20soil%20care%2C%20and%20patient%20observation.%20But%20each%20patch%20of%20green%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20local%20farmers%20to%20return%2C%20grow%20food%2C%20and%20build%20healthier%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20technical%20experiment%20has%20quietly%20grown%20into%20a%20movement%E2%80%94a%20green%20revolution%20that%20not%20only%20cleans%20the%20land%20but%20also%20restores%20livelihoods.%20For%20Dr%20Singh%2C%20this%20work%20is%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20job.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20polluted%2C%20forgotten%20places%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20homes%20for%20trees%2C%20crops%2C%20and%20people%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFly%20ash%2C%20forgotten%20lands%2C%20and%20the%20villages%20that%20paid%20the%20price%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20villages%20near%20the%20thermal%20power%20plants%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Vidarbha%20district%20lived%20under%20a%20cloud%E2%80%94quite%20literally.%20Fly%20ash%20from%20the%20power%20plants%20settled%20on%20their%20crops%2C%20filled%20their%20air%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329441%2Fchennai-startup-bookwater-tracks-water-cans-quality-with-qr-codes-helps-access-safe-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolluted%20their%20water%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20land%2C%20once%20rich%20and%20alive%2C%20slowly%20turned%20into%20a%20dumping%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20seven%20years%20since%20the%20people%20belonging%20to%20adjacent%20villages%20forgot%20about%20the%20fly%20ash%20problem%2C%20the%20air%2C%20soil%2C%20and%20water%20pollution%20it%20caused.%20All%20thanks%20to%20the%20eco%20rejuvenation%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20%3Cstrong%3EDr%20Lal%20Singh%20in%20conversation%20with%20the%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFly%20ash%2C%20a%20fine%20powdery%20waste%20released%20from%20burning%20coal%2C%20was%20dumped%20into%20low-lying%20areas%20near%20the%20power%20plants.%20These%20tailing%20ponds%20became%20large%20pits%20of%20toxic%20waste.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20ash%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20stay%20in%20the%20ponds%E2%80%94it%20blew%20over%20the%20fields%2C%20settled%20on%20crops%2C%20mixed%20into%20the%20water%2C%20and%20filled%20the%20air%20people%20breathed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20the%20fly%20ash%20problem%2C%20farmers%E2%80%99%20productivity%20was%20reduced%20drastically%20as%20the%20fly%20ash%20settled%20on%20their%20crops.%20Women%20had%20no%20livelihood%2C%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20nearby%20villages%20breathed%20bad%20air.%20The%20team%20decided%20to%20eradicate%20all%20the%20problems%20and%20began%20to%20rejuvenate%20dump%20sites%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Lal%20Singh%20explains%2C%20his%20voice%20carrying%20the%20weight%20of%20what%20these%20villages%20had%20suffered.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20damage%20was%20not%20just%20to%20the%20land%E2%80%94it%20affected%20entire%20communities.%20Crops%20failed%2C%20incomes%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20clean%20air%20became%20a%20luxury.%20But%20turning%20things%20around%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20simple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClearing%20the%20lands%20for%20bamboo%20cultivation%20was%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20of%20all%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Singh%20shares.%20The%20soil%20was%20weak%2C%20the%20waste%20was%20thick%2C%20and%20preparing%20the%20ground%20for%20new%20life%20demanded%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20despite%20these%20obstacles%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Dr%20Singh%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20his%20team%20pushed%20forward%E2%80%94step%20by%20step%2C%20tree%20by%20tree%E2%80%94showing%20that%20even%20the%20most%20forgotten%20lands%20could%20be%20brought%20back%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20rejuvenated%20lands%20brought%20new%20life%20to%20farmers%20and%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20farmers%20in%20these%20villages%20struggled%20to%20grow%20their%20crops.%20The%20fly%20ash%20from%20nearby%20power%20plants%20settled%20on%20their%20fields%2C%20coating%20%3Cstrong%3Epulses%2C%20cotton%2C%20and%20soya%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%20a%20fine%20layer%20of%20dust.%20Their%20harvests%20shrank%2C%20their%20incomes%20disappeared%2C%20and%20their%20hope%20slowly%20faded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11zon-1751348883.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FSlide1_1_11