i%20Sahara%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20%3Cstrong%3EKoradi%20Nahadula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20village%20just%2010%20km%20from%20the%20dump%20site.%20Pranali%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20never%20imagined%20this%20dead%20land%20could%20become%20a%20place%20of%20work%20and%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20worked%20here%20for%20the%20last%20seven%20years.%20We%20never%20thought%20this%20place%20would%20transform%20like%20this.%20Today%20we%20have%20clean%20air%2C%20water%2C%20and%20healthy%20soil.%20I%20am%20the%20only%20one%20who%20earns%20in%20my%20family%2C%20and%20I%20also%20got%20a%20job%20because%20of%20this%20project%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Cstrong%3Eshe%20shares%20with%20a%20smile%20that%20carries%20both%20gratitude%20and%20quiet%20strength.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pranali%20now%20earns%20%3Cstrong%3ERs%205000%20a%20month%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20tending%20to%20the%20bamboo%20plantation%2C%20caring%20for%20the%20site%20that%20has%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20cared%20for%20her%20in%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Singh%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20cleaning%20the%20land%20to%20watering%20the%20bamboo%20trees%20and%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20site%2C%20we%20have%2020%20women%20employed.%20All%20these%20women%20are%20employed%20on%20a%20three-year%20contract.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Eco-Rejuvenation%20Technology%20is%20an%20eco-friendly%2C%20cost-effective%20solution%20developed%20by%20CSIR-NEERI%20(Council%20of%20Scientific%20and%20Industrial%20Research%20%E2%80%93%20National%20Environmental%20Engineering%20Research%20Institute).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-23_11zon-1751358635.jpg%