%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcitadel-ken-griffin-cash-trump-tariffs-trade-war-hedge-fund-2025-5%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dbusiness-sf%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26fbclid%3DIwY2xjawLP0FhleHRuA2FlbQIxMQBicmlkETFXT1hiUFZkRno5Y0Z0bWwwAR5FrybXD2HuTsRIfllbP7xXQHXnsTLr9Orzln087CJUTxsMEeCpptOKEUhNZw_aem_z56r2RjXG_0urCkoxV9qlQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFundamental%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20take%20a%20slow%20and%20methodical%20approach%20to%20their%20investment%20decisions.%20Whether%20reviewing%20financial%20statements%20or%20talking%20to%20vendors%20and%20company%20executives%2C%20it%20can%20take%20months%20for%20a%20fundamental%20investor%20to%20reach%20a%20conclusion%20about%20what%20to%20invest%20in%20and%20at%20what%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20anymore.%20Artificial%20intelligence%20is%20changing%20the%20slow%20investing%20game%20popularized%20by%20investors%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-warren-buffett-spends-money-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Berkshire%20Hathaway%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-invest-stock-market-inflation-recession-peter-lynch-magellan-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeter%20Lynch%20of%20Fidelity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20asset%20managers%20have%20long%20used%20machine%20learning%20to%20crunch%20spreadsheets%20and%20detect%20trading%20signals%E2%80%94especially%20in%20quant%20and%20systematic%20strategies%E2%80%94%20these%20tools%20can%20also%20quickly%20digest%20and%20analyze%20vast%20reams%20of%20unstructured%20information%2C%20like%20earnings%20call%20transcripts%2C%20regulatory%20filings%2C%20and%20even%20emails.%20It's%20allowing%20large%20asset%20managers%20to%20make%20fundamental%20investing%20decisions%20faster%20than%20ever%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20firms%20that%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20transform%20their%20investment%20processes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225166650c-76b5-4745-8914-00a4c7f690eb%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20Asset%20Management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20and%20a%20half%20years%20ago%2C%20JPMorgan%20Asset%20Management%20AI%20strategist%20Dillon%20Edwards%20sat%20down%20with%20upward%20of%2050%20portfolio%20managers%20to%20understand%20what%20they%20needed.%20He%20asked%20them%20about%20the%20screens%20they%20use%2C%20the%20questions%20they%20ask%20themselves%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20and%20the%20common%20thread%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20get%20our%20attention%20to%20the%20right%20data%2C%20at%20the%20right%20time%2C%20in%20the%20right%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20request%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20Smart%20Monitor%2C%20which%20Edwards%20described%20as%20%26quot%3BSpotify%20for%20the%20investor.%26quot%3B%20It%20scans%20mountains%20of%20data%20to%20surface%20timely%2C%20relevant%20insights%20for%20the%20firm's%20portfolio%20managers%20and%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmart%20Monitor%20is%20part%20of%20JPMorgan's%20broader%20AI%20build-out%20for%20its%20%243.7%20trillion%20asset%20management%20arm%2C%20which%20is%20hosted%20on%20a%20platform%20called%20Spectrum.%20Another%20tool%20within%20this%20platform%20is%20Moneyball%2C%20which%20helps%20portfolio%20managers%20identify%20and%20correct%20potential%20biases%20in%20their%20investment%20decisions%20by%20analyzing%20historical%20data%20and%20market%20behaviors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20building%20something%20new%20for%20investors%20to%20learn%2C%20Edwards%20and%20his%20team%20focused%20on%20AI%20directly%20into%20the%20process%20that%20investors%20have%20spent%20years%20perfecting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bottom-up%20approach%20has%20helped%20to%20minimize%20AI%20skeptics%3A%20A%20handful%20of%20%26quot%3Bchampion%26quot%3B%20PMs%20worked%20closely%20with%20engineers%20during%20development%20and%20became%20in-house%20unofficial%20salespeople%20who%20market%20it%20to%20their%20own%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20wants%20another%20tool%2C%20another%20thing%20to%20do%2C%20something%20that%20the%20AI%20team%20somehow%20thinks%20is%20going%20to%20be%20helpful%20for%20an%20investor%20without%20empathizing%20with%20what%20they're%20doing%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKristian%20West%2C%20JPMorgan%20Asset%20Management's%20head%20of%20investment%20platform%2C%20said%20the%20firm%20is%20also%20developing%20similar%20tools%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20seeing%20if%20they%20can%20continue%20to%20scale%20the%20quantitative%20process%2C%20or%20data-driven%20systematic%20investing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20area%20where%20we%20think%20it%20is%20just%20pretty%20obvious%2C%20whereas%20technology%20and%20data%20capabilities%20improve%2C%20those%20two%20worlds%20collide%20a%20lot%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e56c5ee-7b3d-43be-b8ee-7949770eb700%5C%22%3EAlliance%20Bernstein%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20fundamental%20investors%E2%80%94portfolio%20managers%20and%20analysts%20who%20base%20long-term%20decisions%20on%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20individual%20companies%E2%80%94this%20marks%20a%20turning%20point%3A%20a%20chance%20to%20move%20faster%20and%20dig%20deeper%2C%20but%20also%20a%20moment%20to%20rethink%20how%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20calls%20this%20evolution%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Biron%20person%26quot%3B%3A%20a%20human%20investor%20enhanced%20by%20AI%20armor.%20Not%20a%20replacement%2C%20but%20an%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAB%20has%20developed%20an%20internal%20chatbot%20called%20AB%20AI%2C%20along%20with%20several%20tools%20to%20help%20pull%20from%20internal%20data%2C%20prep%20for%20company%20meetings%2C%20or%20conduct%20research%20tailored%20to%20the%20manager's%20investment%20philosophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20said%20that%20many%20AB%20analysts%20often%20develop%20their%20own%20AI%20agents%20using%20ChatGPT%20or%20Microsoft%20Copilot%20with%20specific%20prompts%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20run%20an%20analysis%20on%20the%20companies%20in%20their%20sector%20after%20an%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20able%20to%20then%20analyze%20companies%20the%20way%20they%20want%20to%2C%20so%20they%20get%20a%20more%20tailored%20or%20customized%20version%20of%20what%20the%20tool%20can%20provide%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChin%20said%20about%2075%25%20of%20the%20firm's%20over%20500%20investment%20professionals%20are%20using%20their%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20sharing%20stories%20like%20%26quot%3Bit%20takes%20me%20a%20day%20rather%20than%20a%20month%20to%20do%20something%2C%20or%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20this%20insight%20that%20I%20did%20not%20get%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20have%20driven%20others%20to%20try%20it%2C%20said%20Chin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20remaining%2025%25%20who%20haven't%20picked%20up%20AI%2C%20he%20believes%20they%20%26quot%3Bwill%20just%20naturally%20come%20when%20they%20see%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20counterparts%20has%20gotten%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eddc2316-2c89-4799-8168-8ccfa8c80b45%5C%22%3EBlackRock%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20reveal%20from%20BlackRock's%20investor%20day%20last%20month%20shows%20just%20how%20fast%20the%20field%20is%20moving.%20The%20%2411%20trillion%20investing%20behemoth%20has%20launched%20Asimov%2C%20an%20agentic%20AI%20platform%20for%20its%20fundamental%20equity%20business.%20Agentic%20AI%20doesn't%20just%20answer%20questions%20following%20prompts%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20take%20action%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20everyone%20else%20is%20sleeping%20at%20night%2C%20we%20have%20these%20virtual%20AI%20agents%2C%20they're%20scanning%20research%20notes%2C%20company%20filings%2C%20emails%20to%20generate%20portfolio%20insights%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm's%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20Robert%20Goldstein%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hopes%20Asimov%20will%20be%20deployed%20across%20the%20firm%20by%20the%20next%20investor%20day%2C%20offering%20investors%20at%20the%20world's%20biggest%20asset%20manager%20a%20powerful%20teammate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaffaele%20Savi%2C%20its%20global%20head%20of%20systemic%20investing%2C%20underscored%20how%20significantly%20AI%20is%20affecting%20the%20investing%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speed%20and%20power%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Breal-time%2C%20millions%20of%20stimulations%20a%20day%20happening%20in%20the%20background%2C%20developing%20situational%20awareness%26quot%3B%20that%20helps%20ensure%20the%20portfolio%20reflects%20the%20manager's%20intentions%20are%20%26quot%3Bprofound.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20has%20changed%20tremendously%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-speeding-up-fundamental-investing-jpmorgan-alliance-bernstein-blackrock-2025-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751362081000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6862e3e085e81483682d1183%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-speeding-up-fundamental-investing-jpmorgan-alliance-bernstein-blackrock-2025-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Thanks%20to%20AI%2C%20investing%20decisions%20that%20once%20took%20months%20are%20unfolding%20in%20days.%20Inside%20the%20transformation%20at%20JPMorgan%2C%20AllianceBernstein%2C%20and%20beyond.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mabrego%40businessinsider.com%20(Michelle%20Abrego)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-speeding-up-fundamental-investing-jpmorgan-alliance-bernstein-blackrock-2025-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OPPO%20Reno14%20series%20to%20launch%20on%20July%203%2C%20Pad%20SE%20to%20tag%20along%3A%20What%20to%20expect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751362010000%2C%22visua