20nearing%2020%25%20of%20US%20GDP%2C%20with%20up%20to%2025%25%20of%20that%20estimated%20to%20be%20wasted%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20taking%20a%20big%20step%20towards%20medical%20superintelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmustafa-suleyman-microsoft-ai-first-business-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMustafa%20Suleyman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Microsoft's%20AI%20division%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20cases%20used%20in%20the%20study%20are%20%26quot%3Bsome%20of%20the%20toughest%20and%20most%20diagnostically%20complex%26quot%3B%20a%20physician%20can%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuleyman%20previously%20led%20AI%20efforts%20at%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e7ef3242-7ec9-44b8-a77d-f4e153f3ee27%5C%22%3EWill%20AI%20replace%20doctors%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20said%20in%20the%20blog%20post%20that%20AI%20%26quot%3Brepresents%20a%20complement%20to%20doctors%20and%20other%20health%20professionals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20technology%20is%20advancing%20rapidly%2C%20their%20clinical%20roles%20are%20much%20broader%20than%20simply%20making%20a%20diagnosis.%20They%20need%20to%20navigate%20ambiguity%20and%20build%20trust%20with%20patients%20and%20their%20families%20in%20a%20way%20that%20AI%20isn't%20set%20up%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClinical%20roles%20will%2C%20we%20believe%2C%20evolve%20with%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20leaders%20like%20Microsoft%20cofounder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gates-ai-job-shortages-doctors-teachers-work-free-time-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBill%20Gates%20have%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20help%20solve%20the%20long-standing%20shortage%20of%20doctors.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20will%20come%20in%20and%20provide%20medical%20IQ%2C%20and%20there%20won't%20be%20a%20shortage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BPeople%20by%20WTF%26quot%3B%20podcast%20published%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20doctors%20have%20told%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBI%20that%20AI%20can't%20and%20shouldn't%20replace%20clinicians%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-changing-home-care-doctors-clinicians-speedoc-singapore-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20can't%20replicate%20physicians'%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epresence%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20nuanced%20judgment%20in%20uncertain%20or%20complex%20conditions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20Dr.%20Shravan%20Verma%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20Singapore-based%20health%20tech%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatbots%20and%20AI%20tools%20can%20handle%20the%20first%20mile%20of%20care%2C%20but%20they%20must%20escalate%20to%20qualified%20professionals%20when%20needed%2C%20he%20told%20BI%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20AI%20in%20healthcare%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Acmlee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ecmlee%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajsmith%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-diagnosed-accurate-doctors-medicine-study-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751352348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68636386f748d8c055f4b0f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-di