%2C%20part%20of%20the%20restoration%20team%2C%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20work%20on%20traditional%20structures%2C%20we%20need%20to%20see%20to%20it%20that%20there%20is%20an%20integration%20between%20existing%20traditional%20material%20that%20has%20been%20used.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20architects%20have%20formulated%20a%20plan%20of%20action%20using%20the%20original%20architectural%20and%20structural%20drawings%20from%20the%20Kamath%20Design%20Studio%20Archives%20to%20help%20understand%20the%20way%20the%20building%20was%20constructed%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fsustainable-school-muskaan-ngo-mitti-ka-ghar-8-1751289440-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-458437%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20architects%20have%20formulated%20a%20plan%20of%20action%20using%20the%20original%20architectural%20and%20structural%20drawings%20from%20the%20Kamath%20Design%20Studio%20Archives%20to%20help%20understand%20the%20way%20the%20buil