20I%20pop%20in%20at%20least%20ten%20pills%20a%20day%20now.%20From%20medicines%20for%20blood%20pressure%20to%20cholesterol%20and%20blood%20thinners%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prescribed%20so%20many.%20None%20of%20which%20I%20needed%20to%20take%20pre-surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EI%20was%20fairly%20fit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20overweight.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20lean%2C%20and%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20heart%20attack%2C%20my%20BMI%20was%2025%20%E2%80%94%20well%20within%20what%E2%80%99s%20considered%20the%20normal%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20all%20outward%20appearances%2C%20I%20looked%20healthy.%20No%20one%20%E2%80%94%20not%20even%20I%20%E2%80%94%20would%E2%80%99ve%20guessed%20that%20I%20was%20at%20risk.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fit%20the%20image%20most%20people%20have%20of%20someone%20likely%20to%20have%20a%20heart%20attack.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20what%20made%20it%20so%20easy%20to%20overlook%20the%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ram%20celebrating%20his%2033rd%20birthday.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FWhatsApp-Image-2020-10-05-at-4.51.31-PM-1751272527-900x1200.jpeg%20900w%2C%20ht