-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELife%20was%20as%20good%20as%20it%20could%20be%20until%20the%20heart%20attack.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20started%20developing%20a%20lot%20of%20dark%20circles%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20Frequent%20headaches%20during%20the%20last%20three%20months%20were%20also%20a%20given.%20However%2C%20all%20this%20can%20also%20very%20well%20be%20attributed%20to%20being%20a%20new%20parent%20and%20could%20be%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20not%20getting%20enough%20rest%20and%20having%20to%20wake%20up%20at%20all%20odd%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20almost%20seven%20years%2C%20I%20have%20been%20prone%20to%20acidity%2C%20and%20that%20ensured%20that%20I%20ate%20healthy%20and%20had%20most%20of%20my%20meals%20at%20home.%20I%20tried%20not%20to%20miss%20my%20meals%20or%20change%20the%20times%20of%20the%20meals%20too%20much%20to%20ensure%20that%20I%20stayed%20fine.%20I%20did%20consult%20a%20doctor%2Cr%20and%20it%20was%20diagnosed%20to%20be%20GERD%2C%20a%20gastric-related%20issue%2C%20wherein%20the%20stomach%20produces%20more%20acid%20than%20needed.%20With%20medications%2C%20the%20symptoms%20would%20decrease%2C%20but%20it%20was%20something%20that%20kept%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20after%20my%20heart%20attack%2C%20doctors%20mentioned%20that%20I%20was%20perhaps%20confusing%20the%20angina%20pain%20to%20be%20acidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMy%20biggest%20takeaway%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20entire%20experience%20was%20a%20harsh%20reminder%20of%20how%20easily%20we%20take%20our%20bodies%20for%20granted.%20We%20grow%20up%20believing%20that%20serious%20health%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20heart%20problems%20%E2%80%94%20are%20something%20that%20happen%20only%20after%2040%20or%2045.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20was%20mindful%20about%20my%20fitness%2C%20careful%20about%20what%20I%20ate%2C%20and%20did%20everything%20I%20thought%20was%20%E2%80%9Cright.%E2%80%9D%20And%20y